# Per-worker auth state — holds LIVE production session cookies for the
# E2E user (see apps/intranet/e2e/fixtures.ts workerStorageState).
# Already covered by `**/e2e-results/` above; kept explicit so this
# secrets-bearing path stays ignored even if that rule is ever narrowed.
**/e2e-results/.auth/

